Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.67,0:00:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,從前 發生了一場叫「廢棄戰爭」的大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在這場漫長的戰爭中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.26,0:00:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,出現了一群人稱「擊墜王」的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他們帶著白色閃耀的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,將打倒敵人的個數刻在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.45,0:00:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,發揮出了超乎人類智慧的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,隨著和平的到來 擊墜王們便不見了蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,傳說中的擊墜王?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是真人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,慌什麼 一群蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他在虛張聲勢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,仔細想想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,擊墜王是三百年前的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,人類怎麼可能活得這麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:02:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 曹長說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.55,0:03:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,看我們怎麼收拾你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小陽菜 把眼睛閉上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,發生了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,人呢? 你幹了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼搞的?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,人呢? 那傢伙人在哪兒?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,人呢? 卑鄙小人給我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,曹長…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在走路而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 還回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,從她身上奪走的點數
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,她懷著對媽媽的信任走過的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,5年時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:04:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是傳說中的擊墜王 在發脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,竟敢這麼對我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,光殺了你還不夠解氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,看我把你剁成肉醬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼? 我可是天選之人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能有人躲得開我的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能 我的劍是全伊里尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,最快的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,揮舞著等身長的大太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,左手刻著-999點數的 傳說中的擊墜王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他的腳力超乎人類智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,依靠肉眼看不見的動作消滅敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因此得名 「閃擊的擊墜王」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可他的點數不是-999嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,既然是負的 不是很弱嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是他被女生甩掉的次數
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 你睜眼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我在天上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 害怕嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,難以置信 人竟然能在天上飛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,也許吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,果然里希特先生 就是我一直在找的擊墜王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,趕緊收拾掉 把你的點數奪回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你還餓著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,餓著?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,回去以後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我請你吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係 我一定會奪回你的點數
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:07:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是說點數
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你別受傷 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,受傷的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,別亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定會請你吃飯的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,小陽菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我要奪回你的點數
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,回去之後 和你一起吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,說定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.02,0:09:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,要我停手嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,別…別打了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 小陽菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣? 我沒受傷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 手臂還靈活著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,陽菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.91,0:10:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你去找
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,傳說中的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,擊墜王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我終於找到了 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這個我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,撈到個好東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,數字球能賣好大一筆錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這下從明天起我也變有錢人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生真是的 你這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你這女人真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,還不懂嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我的點數是5700
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你是760
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不樂意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要賭星嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一直在找你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼? 不想白給嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這個就給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,迷你嘔吐醬玩偶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我去找擊墜王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,除了我還有別人也被叫做「擊墜王」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你媽媽說的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,小陽菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事啊 小陽菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽的遺物也被拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,現在一頭霧水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,以後該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,小陽菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,總之 這個玩偶先拿著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,玩偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 拿著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你很快就會懂了 該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的數字球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:15:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,數字球這個東西 只要持有就是重罪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,在阿爾西亞 是最重的罪行之一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真像那傻子會幹的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你老老實實把數字球交給軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就不會被問罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但你拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,而且還被軍隊的人看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去 你一輩子都會被軍隊追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:15:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,想要數字球的地痞流氓數不勝數
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不被人奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你這不諳世事的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕連三天的安全都無法保障
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一直
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,都在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,自從媽媽不在以後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我無依無靠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,多少年 多少年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,都一個人在路上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,其實
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我好孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,一個個城鎮找過去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,到頭來 也只是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,覺得自己以後都會孤苦伶仃的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我好孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我在這座鎮上遇見了里希特先生和奈奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常 非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,還是第一次 笑得那麼開心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,回去之後我們一起吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不是說好的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.91,0:18:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你這騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:18:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,到頭來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:18:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,數字球在你手上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 你別誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我本來就對數字球不感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我反倒 是來向你道謝的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,道謝?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.49,0:19:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 多虧了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我們才找到了擊墜王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這下我終於能交出份不錯的報告了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,給真正的長官
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,給真正的長官?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 話說真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,光走路就能把人震飛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,移動速度超過了音速嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:20:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,而最厲害的 就是那個高空下來的劍擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.94,0:20:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不 應該說是「爆擊」嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那個重力加速度根本接不住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就算躲開一點 也會被下落的衝擊波震飛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,該怎麼破…哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,正如您所言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,到底…在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 錯不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我親眼看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,代號001 閃擊的擊墜王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特·巴赫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.95,0:20:54.95,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,730)}「我恨你」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.63,0:22:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊 我是里希特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,下集「星掠者」又是走光狂歡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可這沒辦法啊 說到制服就不得不提內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,說到內褲就不得不提制服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,別說假預告
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.97,0:22:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,下集「這是制服 沒辦法」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.88,0:22:40.40,Next,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1103,840)}下集「這是制服 沒辦法」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.60,0:22:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,————————OP————————
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:20.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}拖著沉重的腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:23.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}行走著尋找希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:28.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}即使受挫 也邁出第一步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.30,0:01:32.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}無法分擔的傷痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:35.10,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}被撕扯的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.10,0:01:40.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}如果需要同伴 我就在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:46.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}每個人都有自己不同的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.65,0:01:54.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}只要和大家一起 感覺任何願望都能成真
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:57.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}{\pos(960,1035)}Forever Plunderer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:02:00.80,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}跟著走 即使迷失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:06.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}也想守護 吹散痛苦的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:12.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}讓跨越未來的堅強 不輸給迎面的風暴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:23.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}匯聚到一起吧 往日各自走過的遙遠路途
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.70,0:01:20.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}重たい足引きずり
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.50,0:01:23.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}歩いて探す希望
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.45,0:01:28.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}めげそうでも 最初の一歩 踏み出そう
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.30,0:01:32.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}別けてくれない痛み
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.40,0:01:35.10,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}千切れそうになる心
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.10,0:01:40.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}誰かを求めるなら ここに私いるから
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.75,0:01:46.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}一人一人違った 星があるから
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.65,0:01:54.05,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}皆と一緒なら どんな夢も叶う気がする
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.00,0:02:00.80,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}付いていく 見失っても
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.80,0:02:06.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}苦しみ吹き荒れる 魂 守りたい
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.50,0:02:12.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}未来を超える強さが 嵐に負けぬように
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.90,0:02:23.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}重ねようよ 別々に 数えた実った遥かな道
